ot;:&quot;Gorgeous, no-expense-spared, fully remodeled 11th-floor luxury condo offering breathtaking water and downtown views. Completely updated since 2023, including a brand-new Bosch A/C installed December 2025, this stunning residence showcases impeccable craftsmanship and high-end finishes throughout. Highlights include epoxy flooring throughout, quartz countertops, custom marble backsplashes, and solid wood custom cabinetry with abundant storage. The chefs kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, including a Sub-Zero refrigerator, Viking French double ovens, Viking induction range and hood, Bosch dishwasher, and microwave, along with a large double pantry featuring pull-out shelving. An electric fireplace with quartz surround adds warmth and elegance to the living space. The dining area features a striking 60-inch marble table seating six, which conveys with the sale and perfectly complements the oversized quartz island. Adjacent is a beautifully designed work desk area with quartz countertops, custom marble backsplash, and illuminated glass-front cabinets. The inside laundry room offers newer stackable washer and dryer, additional storage, and houses the new A/C unit. Nearby is the updated guest bathroom with a walk-in shower and lighted mirror, along with a spacious guest bedroom featuring a walk-in closet and custom Ethan Allen blackout shades for restful nights. On the opposite side of the unit, the living area and exquisite primary retreat both enjoy sweeping water and city views, enhanced by automated window shades. The large primary suite offers his-and-hers closets and a spa-like en-suite bathroom with double custom vanities, illuminated mirrors, porcelain tile, soaking tub, and a walk-in shower with multiple jets and handheld spray. Step onto the expansive balcony to take in picturesque views of the Intracoastal Waterway, Clearwater Memorial Causeway Bridge, and Clearwater Beach. Additional features include Category 5 impact-rated windows, high ceilings, Restoration Hardware chandeliers in the dining and living areas, fresh interior paint, a 2023 tankless water heater, and a massive walk-in storage room just off the entry. The unit includes two assigned under-building parking spaces and a private storage locker. Waters Edge offers exceptional resort-style amenities, including a club room with billiards, bar, private dining area, and full kitchen available for private events; an outdoor patio overlooking the marina, Coachman Park, and The Sound music venue; a heated pool and spa with cabanas, grills, and outdoor fireplace; and a state-of-the-art fitness center with sauna. Ideally located near shopping, dining, and entertainment, and just over the bridge from the world-famous powder sands of Clearwater Beach, this extraordinary residence is truly one of a kind! An absolute must-see!!&quot;,&quot;remarks_private&quot;:&quot;24 Hour Notice. Listing agent must accompany. Call Ryan for showings 727-647-8089&quot;,&quot;sale_rent&quot;:null,&quot;school_district&quot;:null,&quot;school_elementary&quot;:null,&quot;school_high&quot;:null,&quot;school_middle&quot;:null,&quot;showing_inst&quot;:&quot;24 Hour Notice. Listing agent must accompany. Call Ryan for showings 727-647-8089&quot;,&quot;sqft&quot;:1676,&quot;sqft_source&quot;:&quot;Public Records&quot;,&quot;state&quot;:&quot;FL&quot;,&quot;status&quot;:&quot;Active&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null,&quot;subdivision&quot;:&quot;WATERS EDGE CONDO&quot;,&quot;taxes&quot;:13359.0,&quot;updated_at&quot;:&quot;2026-01-06T23:21:49&quot;,&quot;year_built&quot;:2008,&quot;zipcode&quot;:&quot;33755&quot;,&quot;zip&quot;:&quot;33755&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[&quot;https://dvvjkgh94f2v6.cloudfront.net/735d922b/777256876/83dcefb7.jpeg&quot;,&quot;https://dvvjkgh94f2v6.cloudfront.net/735d922b/777256876/1ad5be0d.jpeg&quot;,&quot;https://dvvjkgh94f2v6.cloudfront.net/735d922b/777256876/6dd28e9b.jpeg&quot;,&quot;https://dvvjkgh94f2v6.cloudfront.net/735d922b/777256876/f3b61b38